\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 {\f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 15.} On 16 February 2012, pursuant to Order 20 rule 1 of the Rules of the High Court (Cap 4A), Mr Raj [then represented by Messrs David Ravenscroft & Co ("DRC"), solicitors assigned by the Director of Legal Aid] amended the writ of summons to make Sam Lee the 1st defendant and add Yick Hing as the 2nd defendant to this action.\par}

