\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 {\f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 23.} On 11 June 2014, Mr Raj re-amended the statement of claim to, {\f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i \strike0 \ul0 inter alia}, put forward the case that he was employed by Sam Lee and/or Yick Hing at the time of the accident. Paragraph 4 (which pleads the occurrence of the accident as set out in paragraph 16 above) however remains untouched by this further round of amendments.\par}

